  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to the Land of Fateful Threads, Carmera...</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have been summoned to the Sky Town of another world, where dark meteors rain from the heavens, spreading chaos and corruption.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Monster Girl Saga: Fallen Heroes</strong> is an open-world action RPG where you face off against fallen heroes, once allies of the monster girls, now consumed by distorted love and the power of the Dark Runestone. Your mission is to rescue the monster girls, rebuild your village, and save the world from impending doom.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Thrilling Combat Against Fallen Heroes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The fallen heroes, former allies of the monster girls, are beings tainted by the power of the Dark Runestone. Overcome their formidable abilities and rescue the monster girls.<br>Recruited monster girls can join your party, allowing you to switch between characters mid-battle to utilize diverse skills and combat styles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459850/extras/05d30f78896f1ae083e256fba292388f.poster.avif?t=1743415209\" width=720 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459850/extras/05d30f78896f1ae083e256fba292388f.webm?t=1743415209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459850/extras/05d30f78896f1ae083e256fba292388f.mp4?t=1743415209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Vibrant Open World</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a dynamic world where the passage of time and real-time weather changes shape your journey. Explore diverse landscapes, from sunlit forests to stormy ruins, each offering fresh challenges, secrets, and rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459850/extras/ad488104cc0a88099c8cf680681b6c22.poster.avif?t=1743415209\" width=720 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459850/extras/ad488104cc0a88099c8cf680681b6c22.webm?t=1743415209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459850/extras/ad488104cc0a88099c8cf680681b6c22.mp4?t=1743415209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Experience the thrill of movement in Sky Town!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sky Lake Waterslide Park:</strong> Experience the thrill of high-speed slides in a floating amusement park above Sky Lake! Twist, turn, and race through the air on gravity-defying tracks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459850/extras/140500414b77818529daa76343064b90.poster.avif?t=1743415209\" width=720 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459850/extras/140500414b77818529daa76343064b90.webm?t=1743415209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459850/extras/140500414b77818529daa76343064b90.mp4?t=1743415209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Glide with the Updraft:</strong> Catch powerful updrafts to ascend high into the sky, reaching hidden Sky Islands floating above the world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459850/extras/2cd58b3451c177145f01a30097860a9c.poster.avif?t=1743415209\" width=720 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459850/extras/2cd58b3451c177145f01a30097860a9c.webm?t=1743415209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459850/extras/2cd58b3451c177145f01a30097860a9c.mp4?t=1743415209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dive into the Unknown:</strong> Plunge into the depths of lakes and uncover ancient secrets hidden beneath the surface. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459850/extras/2eda761908c5e052f03497637acbf2bb.poster.avif?t=1743415209\" width=720 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459850/extras/2eda761908c5e052f03497637acbf2bb.webm?t=1743415209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459850/extras/2eda761908c5e052f03497637acbf2bb.mp4?t=1743415209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Diverse Job System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rebuild a thriving village by assigning rescued monster girls to various jobs, such as farmers, blacksmiths, and alchemists.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Farmers</strong> cultivate crops to sustain the village.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Blacksmiths</strong> mine and forge materials for equipment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Alchemists</strong> create potions to aid in your quest.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each job contributes to restoring life and prosperity to the once-ruined land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459850/extras/210af3df9b60ee0bdd47ce9fa3cabb9c.poster.avif?t=1743415209\" width=720 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459850/extras/210af3df9b60ee0bdd47ce9fa3cabb9c.webm?t=1743415209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459850/extras/210af3df9b60ee0bdd47ce9fa3cabb9c.mp4?t=1743415209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Interactive Relationships with Monster Girls</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build bonds with the monster girls you save. Overwork them, and they may become tired or refuse to work.Cheer them up through rock-paper-scissors, heartfelt interactions, or even a simple hug. Your care and attention can reignite their spirits and strengthen your team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459850/extras/d0a5d7c46bf7e3d82f7cbf312d9d589b.poster.avif?t=1743415209\" width=720 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459850/extras/d0a5d7c46bf7e3d82f7cbf312d9d589b.webm?t=1743415209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459850/extras/d0a5d7c46bf7e3d82f7cbf312d9d589b.mp4?t=1743415209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Unique Charm of Indie Solo Development</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crafted with passion by a solo indie developer, this game offers a deeply personal experience. From its richly detailed world to its innovative mechanics and emotionally compelling story, </p>",
